plot: In this comedy, a naive, strikingly beautiful girl from Uzbekistan, comes to America. Once here, she rides a crazy road that is inhabited by sex addicts, lonely men, photographers, rap stars, preachers, web masters and strippers.
title: Natasha Kizmet: The Movie
